"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-olympics-opening-ceremony-fitting-tribute-paris-people\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Check out Sports Illustrated\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Daily Rings, our daily Olympics podcast from Mitch Goldich and Dan Gartland.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 83, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.1502010156428799e-12, \"text\": \"Mitch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Mitch\"}, {\"begin\": 100, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gartland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999290594, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gartland\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gartland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gartland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports Illustrated\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Daily Rings\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 44}, {\"ngram\": \"our daily Olympics\", \"from\": 46, \"to\": 64}, {\"ngram\": \"podcast\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 72}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe wherever you get your podcasts (Apple,\\u00c2Spotify) and find clips on\\u00c2SI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s YouTube page.\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 0.9999965958471609, \"rank\": 3.400118001483323e-06, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your podcasts\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2Spotify\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 166}, {\"ngram\": \"clips\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 For a while, in the days leading up to Friday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Olympics opening ceremony, Paris in 2024 felt like Tokyo in \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009821 or Beijing in \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009822: the crowds emptied out, silent but for wind drifting through barren squares.\\u00c2 But then\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094gr\\u00c3\\u00a2ce \\u00c3 Dieu\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094police opened the barriers, and for the first Olympics since Pyeongchang, in 2018, fans poured in.\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4039843680606862e-37, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999993175836207, \"rank\": 6.821951303249024e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"score\": 0.9994429795397907, \"rank\": 0.0005573309046482145, \"text\": \"Pyeongchang\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the days\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 242}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 267}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009821\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"wind\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"barren squares\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"then\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094gr\\u00c3\\u00a2ce \\u00c3 Dieu\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094police\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"the barriers\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Olympics\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some 300,000 of them gathered along the banks of the Seine, huddling under umbrellas and waving flags.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.097784393174308e-31, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"umbrellas\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They leaned out of Mansard windows and held banners off balconies.\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mansard_roof\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mansard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mansard_roof\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mansard_roof\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"banners\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"balconies\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They watched from restaurants overlooking the water and on TV at caf\\u00c3\\u00a9s far from the city center.\\u00c2 Thegoal of the Opening Ceremony,organizers said before the event, was to celebrate the city of Paris, and it did that, with athletes in bateaux-mouches wending their way down the Seine, past the Louvre and Notre-Dame toward the Eiffel Tower, while performers leapt on bridges and rooftops, despite a downpour.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999984249055741, \"rank\": 1.5507491666940949e-06, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4039843680606862e-37, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.097784393174308e-31, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1026, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"score\": 0.9828737097303081, \"rank\": 0.01742471092655428, \"text\": \"Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"caf\\u00c3\\u00a9\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"the city center\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"bateaux-mouches\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"performers\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"bridges\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"rooftops\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"a downpour\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the truest tribute it could offer was to the people of the host city, who live life in public.\\u00c2 It was for this reason that the terrorist attacks of Nov. 13, 2015\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094which killed 130 and injured 416 at a stadium, a theater and half a dozen caf\\u00c3\\u00a9s and restaurants\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094so shook Parisians.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the truest tribute\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"the host city\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"public\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"this reason\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"the terrorist attacks\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"Nov.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"2015\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094which\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"a theater\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"half a dozen\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"caf\\u00c3\\u00a9\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094so\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a people that offers discounted museum tickets to the unemployed; everyone, they believe, should have access to culture.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a people\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"discounted museum tickets\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those public spaces are crucial in a city whose average apartment size barely tops 600 square feet, and any threat to them constitutes a threat to the city itself.\\u00c2 And indeed there were threats this week: A Russian chef was arrested on Sunday on suspicion of plotting with foreign authorities to stage acts of \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cdestabilization\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d during the Games.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.7625217790266968, \"rank\": 0.3112845825192032, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those public spaces\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"whose average apartment size\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"600 square feet\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"any threat\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"a threat\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"suspicion\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"foreign authorities\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"acts\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Early Friday morning, a series of coordinated arson attacks shut down major railways into and out of Paris, causing chaos but no injuries.\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2012, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4039843680606862e-37, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"coordinated arson attacks\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"major railways\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1995}, {\"ngram\": \"chaos\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"no injuries\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(And not directly affecting the Olympics; none of the areas targeted\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Courtalain, southwest of Paris; Croisilles, to the north; and Pagny-sur-Moselle, to the east\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094are within 60 miles of the capital.)\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2146, \"end\": 2151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4039843680606862e-37, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pagny-sur-Moselle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pagny-sur-Moselle\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pagny-sur-Moselle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pagny-sur-Moselle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"the areas\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"Croisilles\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"the north\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"the east\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094are\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"60 miles\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials estimated some 45,000 police had been deployed across Paris on Friday.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4039843680606862e-37, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Officials\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"some 45,000 police\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parisians griped about having to show government-issued QR codes to access their homes and workplaces.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"government-issued QR codes\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2398}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2420}, {\"ngram\": \"workplaces\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These Olympics, as are most Olympics, have been controversial among the locals, with their focus on clearing out homeless people and cleaning up the neglected suburbs only now that foreigners might visit them.\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These Olympics\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"most Olympics\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"the locals\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"their focus\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"homeless people\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2565}, {\"ngram\": \"the neglected suburbs\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2603}, {\"ngram\": \"foreigners\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many disgruntled Parisians left the city entirely.\\u00c2 Those who stayed saw the show of a lifetime on Friday.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many disgruntled Parisians\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tokyo and Beijing Olympics deserved fans, too.\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2759, \"end\": 2764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999993175836207, \"rank\": 6.821951303249024e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2769, \"end\": 2785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.425641799858186e-17, \"text\": \"Beijing Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Paris got them, and they brought the ceremony to life.\\u00c2 This was the first Opening Ceremony to take place through an entire city rather than in a stadium, which in some ways made it perfect for television\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094no one present got to see everything.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 3055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2810, \"end\": 2815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4039843680606862e-37, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2855}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Opening Ceremony\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2901}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"an entire city\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2938}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2963}, {\"ngram\": \"some ways\", \"from\