\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A dozen headless Marie Antoinettes danced in the windows of La Conciergerie, where the country\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s final queen was imprisoned before she met the guillotine.\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3412, \"end\": 3424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8481089647466194e-52, \"text\": \"Conciergerie\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A dozen headless Marie Antoinettes\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"the windows\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3405}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s final queen\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"the guillotine\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A gendarme dressed as Joan of Arc rode a metal horse down the Seine.\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3568, \"end\": 3573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.097784393174308e-31, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A gendarme\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3516}, {\"ngram\": \"Joan\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3532}, {\"ngram\": \"Arc\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3539}, {\"ngram\": \"a metal horse\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in this moment of high tension, amid a snap election that has essentially left the country without a government, the ceremony also took care to include groups historically marginalized in French society: French Moroccan comedian Jamel Debbouze and soccer star Zinedine Zidane, who is of Algerian descent, met and handed the Olympic torch off to a group of kids who ran through neighb